content.description:
Locate a sloping hold above head level, near the diagonal crack on the left end of the wall. Start matching on the sloper, and traverse right along a line of newly cleaned slopers for 15-20' or so until you can turn onto a slab that faces west (behind

Arrowhead Arete

). Some variations have yet to be cleaned, and eventually this will be a nice wall to warm up on.
